item.title: CVE-2018-1056|2024-08-05T03:44:11.827Z -- amadvance -- advancecomp%3A
item.description: An out-of-bounds heap buffer read flaw was found in the way advancecomp before 2.1-2018/02 handled processing of ZIP files. An attacker could potentially use this flaw to crash the advzip utility by tricking it into processing crafted ZIP files.
